UID:cVQxtgdToEw0iW13JJ7b9
SUMMARY:Spy Masters Academy
DTSTAMP:20260402T030256Z
DTSTART:20260406T163000Z
DESCRIPTION:Class Experience Calling all young secret agents! This time kid
	s are welcome to join action-packed Outdoor Spy Camp\, where kids will tra
	in to become top-notch spies through thrilling challenges\, daring mission
	s\, and teamwork! Obstacle Courses & Ninja Training – Agents-in-training w
	ill test their agility\, speed\, and stealth as they navigate exciting nin
	ja courses\, crawl through the forest and learn to use nature objects to c
	omplete the challenge. Scavenger Hunts & Riddle Solving – Spies must sharp
	en their detective skills by decoding secret messages\, solving riddles\, 
	and uncovering hidden clues to complete their top-secret missions. Nerf Ba
	ttles & Tactical Challenges – Gear up for friendly Nerf wars\, where teamw
	ork and strategy are key to outsmarting the opposition. Agents will also p
	ractice their precision and accuracy with target practice and stealth mane
	uvers. Escape Room-Style Puzzles – Secret agents will work together to cra
	ck codes\, unlock treasure chests\, and solve mind-bending puzzles before 
	time runs out! Outdoor Adventure & Camouflage Training – Spies will blend 
	into their surroundings\, practice silent movement\, and use nature to the
	ir advantage while completing their missions. This high-energy camp is per
	fect for kids who love adventure\, problem-solving\, and action-packed fun
	 in the great outdoors! Are you ready to accept the mission? - follow the 
	ticket link to book the camp!\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/det
	ails/spy-masters-academy/18306067/2026-04-06T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Sports 
